          "Max Hoffman, an American importer of European luxury and sports cars, is the one who receives credit for dreaming up the BMW 507. It would undercut the expensive "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            5
          ],
          1,
          "Mercedes 300SL"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
