        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            7
          ],
          1,
          "BMW"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " 502. With a peak 155-horsepower and ZF four-speed manual transmission, plus reasonably good handling, the 507 promised a lot of fun on the road. Plus, you could get a detachable hardtop instead of opting for the soft top."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      3
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Originally, Hoffman envisioned "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            8
          ],
          1,
          "BMW"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " cranking out 5,500 of these cars a year. Considering "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            9
          ],
          1,
